details.name: Doom
details.description: Inflicts a curse that prevents an enemy Hero from casting spells or using items, while taking damage over time. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter. DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel
details.upgrade_description: Will suspend Doom's duration while the affected unit is within 900 range. Also causes it to remove positive buffs from the target when cast, and break most passive abilities while active.
